{"questionId":"9338","questionHtml":"<p>Using the Maclaurin series for <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{arctan}}\\,x\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>arctan</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n</math></span> and <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{{\\text{e}}^{3x}} - 1\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>e</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>3</mn>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span>, find the Maclaurin series for <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{arctan}}\\left( {{{\\text{e}}^{3x}} - 1} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>arctan</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>e</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n          </mrow>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> up to and including the <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{x^3}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> term.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>substituting <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"3x\">\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n</math></span> into the Maclaurin series for <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{{\\text{e}}^x}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>e</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{{\\text{e}}^{3x}} = 1 + 3x + \\frac{{{{\\left( {3x} \\right)}^2}}}{{2{\\text{!}}}} + \\frac{{{{\\left( {3x} \\right)}^3}}}{{3{\\text{!}}}} +&nbsp; \\ldots \">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>e</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>3</mn>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>(</mo>\n              <mrow>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>)</mo>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>!</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>(</mo>\n              <mrow>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>)</mo>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>!</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mo>…</mo>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>substituting <span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {{{\\text{e}}^{3x}} - 1} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>e</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n          </mrow>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></span> into the Maclaurin series for <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{arctan}}\\,x\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>arctan</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{arctan}}\\left( {{{\\text{e}}^{3x}} - 1} \\right) = \\left( {{{\\text{e}}^{3x}} - 1} \\right) - \\frac{{{{\\left( {{{\\text{e}}^{3x}} - 1} \\right)}^3}}}{3} + \\frac{{{{\\left( {{{\\text{e}}^{3x}} - 1} \\right)}^5}}}{5} -&nbsp; \\ldots \">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>arctan</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>e</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n          </mrow>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>e</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n          </mrow>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>(</mo>\n              <mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <msup>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mtext>e</mtext>\n                    </mrow>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mn>3</mn>\n                      <mi>x</mi>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </msup>\n                </mrow>\n                <mo>−</mo>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>)</mo>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>(</mo>\n              <mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <msup>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mtext>e</mtext>\n                    </mrow>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mn>3</mn>\n                      <mi>x</mi>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </msup>\n                </mrow>\n                <mo>−</mo>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>)</mo>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>5</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>5</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mo>…</mo>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = \\left( {3x + \\frac{{{{\\left( {3x} \\right)}^2}}}{{2{\\text{!}}}} + \\frac{{{{\\left( {3x} \\right)}^3}}}{{3{\\text{!}}}} +&nbsp; \\ldots } \\right) - \\frac{{{{\\left( {3x + \\frac{{{{\\left( {3x} \\right)}^2}}}{{2{\\text{!}}}} + \\frac{{{{\\left( {3x} \\right)}^3}}}{{3{\\text{!}}}} +&nbsp; \\ldots } \\right)}^3}}}{3} +&nbsp; \\ldots \">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>(</mo>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mo>)</mo>\n                </mrow>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>!</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mfrac>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>(</mo>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mo>)</mo>\n                </mrow>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>!</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mfrac>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mo>…</mo>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>(</mo>\n              <mrow>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo>+</mo>\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <msup>\n                        <mrow>\n                          <mrow>\n                            <mo>(</mo>\n                            <mrow>\n                              <mn>3</mn>\n                              <mi>x</mi>\n                            </mrow>\n                            <mo>)</mo>\n                          </mrow>\n                        </mrow>\n                        <mn>2</mn>\n                      </msup>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mtext>!</mtext>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </mrow>\n                </mfrac>\n                <mo>+</mo>\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <msup>\n                        <mrow>\n                          <mrow>\n                            <mo>(</mo>\n                            <mrow>\n                              <mn>3</mn>\n                              <mi>x</mi>\n                            </mrow>\n                            <mo>)</mo>\n                          </mrow>\n                        </mrow>\n                        <mn>3</mn>\n                      </msup>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mtext>!</mtext>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </mrow>\n                </mfrac>\n                <mo>+</mo>\n                <mo>…</mo>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>)</mo>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mo>…</mo>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>selecting correct terms from above&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = \\left( {3x + \\frac{{{{\\left( {3x} \\right)}^2}}}{{2{\\text{!}}}} + \\frac{{{{\\left( {3x} \\right)}^3}}}{{3{\\text{!}}}}} \\right) - \\frac{{{{\\left( {3x} \\right)}^3}}}{3}\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>(</mo>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mo>)</mo>\n                </mrow>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>!</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mfrac>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>(</mo>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mo>)</mo>\n                </mrow>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>!</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mfrac>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>(</mo>\n              <mrow>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>)</mo>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = 3x + \\frac{{9{x^2}}}{2} - \\frac{{9{x^3}}}{2}\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>9</mn>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>9</mn>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[6 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9338","referenceCode":"SPM.1.AHL.TZ0.12c","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Using the Maclaurin series for arctan x and e 3 x − 1 , find the Maclaurin series for arctan ( e 3 x − 1 ) up to and including the x 3 term.","paper":"1","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"c","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 6]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5 —Calculus","Topic 5 —Calculus","AHL 5.19—Maclaurin series"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}